  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to develop, verify and optimize the ERAS protocol for cardiac&#xD;
      surgery.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to develop, verify and optimize the ERAS protocol for cardiac&#xD;
      surgery, thereby improving the overall prognosis of cardiac surgery patients, reducing the&#xD;
      incidence of complications, and shortening the length of hospital stay.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
